data.description: Looking for an affordable move-in ready home w/ a brand new roof on it? If so, this is the one for you! This charming home features 2 bedrooms (plus an office), 1 bathroom (shower/tub combo w/ subway tile backsplash, large vanity, & granite countertops), 1325 sq ft, hardwood flooring throughout, large kitchen w/ tile flooring, hickory cabinets, stainless steel appliances, & granite countertops, attached 1 car garage w/ shop space, spacious 0.13 acre lot, detached shop, RV parking, & much more! This is a perfect opportunity for a buyer (qualifies for FHA or VA financing) that needs ample storage & low maintenance. Contact your agent today for a personal tour, before it's too late!
